        %p The Bluhm/Helfand Social Innovation Fellowship @ Chicago Ideas Week recognizes a group of young socially-conscious leaders who have developed sustainable ventures addressing social needs, and provide them with exposure to nationally recognized business and community leaders, funding to support their cause, and a platform for growth.
